ORG 100
LOAD X2       / Load shortest process first
LOOP1, SUBT ONE
       SKIPCOND 000
       JUMP LOOP1
LOAD X3       / Load next shortest process
LOOP2, SUBT ONE
       SKIPCOND 000
       JUMP LOOP2
LOAD X1       / Load longest process last
LOOP3, SUBT ONE
       SKIPCOND 000
       JUMP LOOP3


X1, DEC 5
X2, DEC 3
X3, DEC 4
ONE, DEC 1
